headline: Is It Time to Buy the Super Micro Stock Dip?
summary: After two straight days of selling, Super Micro stock is wavering in Thursday morning trading.  The stock might avoid being delisted from the Nasdaq stock exchange—but it looks destined to be removed from the  index.  Both issues have been at the top of investors’ minds.
